Package com.jswiff.xml

Class Summary
Transformer This class offers simple methods for translation between SWF and XML.
XMLReader Converts an XML file to a SWF document.
XMLWriter This class converts an SWF document to XML.
 

Exception Summary
MalformedElementException Indicates that an element is malformed.
MissingAttributeException Indicates that a mandatory attribute is missing within a specific parent element.
MissingElementException Indicates that a mandatory element is missing within a specific parent element.
MissingNodeException Indicates that a mandatory node is missing.
